---
const items = [
  { label: 'UK-Based folks',            desc: 'because our teaching revolves around sourcing products from UK suppliers only.' },
  { label: 'Financial freedom seekers', desc: 'tired of selling their time living pay cheque to pay cheque and want something better for the long term.' },
  { label: 'Halal income',              desc: 'those who want to generate money that is halal through a legit and proven way.' },
  { label: 'Fed up with gurus',         desc: 'those tired of course sellers robbing them of both their money and time on mediocre knowledge.' },
  { label: 'Stressed mums',             desc: "mothers who could really use this opportunity to spend time with their children at home without worrying about income." },
  { label: 'Action takers',             desc: "we're giving you the tools to succeed, the rest depends on how much effort and commitment you're willing to put into your business — and even if you fail at first, we'll make sure you don't." },
  { label: 'Complete newbies',          desc: 'this bootcamp was built with a curriculum for people with no experience to succeed, regardless of their technical skills and prior education.' },
];
---

<section class="wiif" id="who-is-it-for">
  <div class="wiif-inner">

    <div class="wiif-header">
      <h2 class="display-headline wiif-headline reveal">
        Who Is This<br /><em>Bootcamp For?</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="wiif-intro-block">
      <p class="wiif-intro reveal">
        If you live in the UK, tired of selling your time in a 9 to 5, surviving from pay check to
        pay check, you've been searching for a halal way to make income from your own surroundings
        so you can quit your stressful job that's been robbing you the time you could have spent
        with your loved ones or used to explore and live life on your own time.
      </p>
      <p class="wiif-intro wiif-intro--em reveal">
        Then this Bootcamp is hosted specifically for you!
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="wiif-this-is reveal">This is for</p>

    <ul class="wiif-list">
      {items.map((item, i) => (
        <li class="wiif-item reveal" style={`transition-delay: ${i * 0.06}s`}>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-check wiif-check"></i>
          <span><strong>{item.label}</strong> — {item.desc}</span>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .wiif {
    background: var(--color-near-black);
    padding: 130px 0 110px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .wiif::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(212,165,116,0.25), transparent);
  }

  .wiif-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 60px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .wiif-header {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .wiif-headline {
    font-size: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 64px);
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.08;
  }

  .wiif-headline em {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── Intro ── */
  .wiif-intro-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  .wiif-intro {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
  }

  .wiif-intro--em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .wiif-this-is {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* ── List ── */
  .wiif-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .wiif-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .wiif-item strong {
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .wiif-check {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-size: 13px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .wiif { padding: 72px 0 64px; }
    .wiif-inner { padding: 0 24px; }
    .wiif-intro { font-size: 16px; }
    .wiif-intro--em { font-size: 17px; }
    .wiif-item { font-size: 15px; }
    .wiif-header { margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .wiif-intro-block { gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 36px; padding-bottom: 36px; }
  }
</style>
